---
// Brief mention of other channels (SMS and WhatsApp)
---

<section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-nexus-tech mb-4">
          E não paramos por aí: <span class="text-nexus-respect">SMS</span> e <span class="text-nexus-creative">WhatsApp</span> também disponíveis
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          A NEXUS oferece um ecossistema completo de comunicação. Combine canais para uma estratégia imbatível.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- SMS Card -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow border-t-4 border-nexus-respect">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-nexus-respect/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-nexus-respect" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-nexus-tech">SMS</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Alcance e Velocidade</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-nexus-respect flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">98% de taxa de abertura</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-nexus-respect flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Entrega instantânea</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-nexus-respect flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Ideal para alertas e cupons</span>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            Perfeito para lembretes de última hora, códigos de cupom exclusivos e comunicados urgentes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- WhatsApp Card -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow border-t-4 border-nexus-creative">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-nexus-creative/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-nexus-creative" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.890-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-nexus-tech">WhatsApp</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Engajamento Rico</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-nexus-creative flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Catálogos visuais de produtos</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-nexus-creative flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Atendimento conversacional</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-nexus-creative flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Mídia rica (fotos, vídeos, áudios)</span>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            Conecte-se onde seus clientes já estão. Construa relacionamento que gera vendas.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA for multi-channel -->
      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <strong class="text-nexus-respect">RCS</strong> como destaque,
          <strong class="text-nexus-tech">SMS</strong> para urgência,
          <strong class="text-nexus-creative">WhatsApp</strong> para relacionamento.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 italic">
          A combinação perfeita para dominar a Black Friday.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
